query:
-- Check user's plan
SELECT u.id, u.email, u.planId, p.name as planName, p.maxKeys, p.maxFolders 
FROM users u 
JOIN plans p ON u.planId = p.id 
LIMIT 5;

-- Check all plans
SELECT id, name, maxKeys, maxFolders, price FROM plans ORDER BY price;
